    #include<iostream>
    using namespace std;
    int main()
    {
    	int t,n,c;
    	cin>>t;
    	while(t>0)
    	{
    		cin>>n>>c;
    		int a[n],sum=0;
    		for(int i=0;i<n;i++)
    		{
    		cin>>a[i];
    		sum=sum+a[i];
    		}
    		if(c>=sum)
    		cout<<"Yes"<<endl;
    		else
    		cout<<"No"<<endl;
    		t--;
    	}
    	return 0;
    }
